cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "spatial-cluster-compare"
abstract: >-
  Automated clustering algorithm comparison pipeline for spatial proteomics,
  cytometry data, or any numerical feature table. Runs several clustering
  algorithms on the same data, scores each one on multiple complementary
  metrics (including bootstrap stability), and selects the best method
  through a transparent, reproducible composite score.
authors:
